# Production environment for the Vue build (native VPS, two-domain setup).
# Copy to frontend/.env on the server before running `npm run build`.
#
# The API lives on its own subdomain, so this is the API origin WITHOUT the /api
# suffix (the HTTP client already prefixes requests with /api). Because the SPA
# and API are on different origins, the API allows this origin via CORS
# (see backend FRONTEND_URLS).
VITE_API_URL=https://api.champions.ferzendervarli.com
